The uncle of boxer Tyson Fury, and brother of respected trainer Peter Fury, has died following months in intensive care.

Hughie Fury underwent routine surgery to place a pin below his knee in July, but a blood clot developed following surgery and left him in intensive care. Sadly, Hughie, has now passed away.

His nephew tweeted: 'Tragic loss for the fury family. Uncle Highie Fury. Forever in my heart & life. RIP. Gone to see Jesus.'

